<section id="quickstart">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Get Started</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Two Commands to Guardrails</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Install the plugin, run the wizard, and you're enforcing architecture immediately.
      </p>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Add the marketplace</h3>
            <div class="terminal">
              <div class="terminal-header">
                <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
                <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
                <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
                <span class="terminal-title">Claude Code</span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-body">
                <span class="prompt">&gt;</span> /plugin marketplace add viewyonder/claude-coherence
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Install the plugin</h3>
            <div class="terminal">
              <div class="terminal-header">
                <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
                <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
                <span class="terminal-dot"></span>
                <span class="terminal-title">Claude Code</span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-body">
                <span class="prompt">&gt;</span> /plugin install coherence
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Run <code>/coherence</code></h3>
            <p>The wizard scans your project, asks a few questions, and generates hooks, agents, skills, and CLAUDE.md â€” customized to your stack.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Review &amp; customize</h3>
            <p>Check the generated <code>// === CONFIGURATION ===</code> blocks. Tweak patterns, paths, and thresholds for your project. <a href="/getting-started">Full guide &rarr;</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--cyan);
    border: 2px solid var(--cyan);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .step-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .step-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .step-content .terminal {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>
